<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The actual Purple Headband quest calls for the following:<BR>
<BR>
Dagger of Marnek - Found in Befallen <BR>
                   (Bought mine 50pp)<BR>
<BR>
Skull of Jhen`Tra - Found in Lake of Rathetear           <BR>
                    (Guildmate gave to me)<BR>
<BR>
Coronet of Buried Blood - Found in Permafrost<BR>
                          (Friend gave to me)<BR>
<BR>
Red headband - Gotten through previous quests.<BR>
<BR>
  Turn all these into the Monk in Qeynos.  <BR>
<BR>
  My question is as you can see the Coronet carries a different name.  Are you absolutely certain that the Coronet of Buried Blood is the same as Zaharn's Coronet.  i'd truly hate to lose all that time and effort it took to get the previous headbands.<BR>
<BR>
Thank You<BR>
Ranlador<BR>
